## 3. Risk Assessment & Mitigation

### High-Priority Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation Strategy |
|------|------------|--------|---------------------|
| **Cascade algorithm stack overflow on large grids** | Medium | High | Use iterative BFS instead of recursion; implement visited tracking |
| **State mutation bugs causing UI inconsistencies** | Medium | High | Use immutable updates everywhere; consider Immer library if issues persist |
| **First-click mine placement fails edge cases** | Low | High | Extensive testing of corner/edge first clicks; validate safe zone calculation |
| **TypeScript configuration issues blocking development** | Low | Medium | Use strict mode from start; verify tsconfig settings match Vite template |

### Medium-Priority Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation Strategy |
|------|------------|--------|---------------------|
| **Performance issues on expert grid (480 cells)** | Medium | Medium | Profile cascade algorithm; optimize rendering with React.memo if needed |
| **Tailwind CSS not purging correctly** | Low | Low | Verify content paths in tailwind.config.js |
| **Grid layout breaks on different screen sizes** | Medium | Low | Defer responsive design to Sprint 5; focus on 1920x1080 desktop for Sprint 1 |

